name: VersionState
shortdesc: The version state of the file in Version Cue.

property.name: PROJECT_FILE_NEWER
property.shortdesc: The project has a newer file.

property.name: LOCAL_PROJECT_MATCH
property.shortdesc: The version is identical to the project.

property.name: LOCAL_NEWER
property.shortdesc: The version has modifications that make it newer than the project.

property.name: VERSION_CONFLICT
property.shortdesc: The version contains local edits but the project file is newer.

property.name: NO_RESOURCE
property.shortdesc: No resource and no local file.
